    Every 4 weeks we release stable releases which include bug and security fix backports.
    %a{'href' => 'lts'}
      Learn more…
  %div.details
    %a.app-button.app-button--primary{:href=>'/changelog-stable'}
      Changelog
    %a.app-button{:href=>'/doc/upgrade-guide'}
      Upgrade Guide
    %a.app-button{:href=>'https://get.jenkins.io/war-stable/'}
      Past Releases

  %h4
    Weekly releases
  %p.app-description
